<item>
            <title>[LU-12539] Pass --with-o2ib option along when building deb packages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12539</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When building deb packages (make debs), &apos;--with-o2ib&apos; option is not passed to ./configure called by package mechanism. So Lustre is possibly built against wrong OFED headers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will push a patch to address this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
